變成 invalid<br />\n<br />\n而所謂嘅掘擴，其實就係用買家同賣家嘅編號去解返開個#hash<br />\n<br />\n口      hash #1890e<br />\n<br />\n買家 18<br />\n賣家 90e<br />\n(真實上係用formula計，我只係簡單講)<br />\n咁樣ching就用到18同90e解到個#hash<br />\n<br />\n如果成功解鎖到就驗證到係valid嘅行為<br />\n解鎖去驗證個人就會收到少量coin作為幫助驗證嘅報酬，俗稱掘礦"},{"pid":"9f32bb62ed5909fb6fd13d625006f1d5fc0fec6a","tid":795324,"uid":36138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e350275ff25a454eec6b8448fe631db9f217fce3","tid":795324,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b869707be0b56f3fd77dc2ddc52c8bccd7e65a5","tid":795324,"uid":36138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"789a8370d31b2008d1dca3eeef67ae4aa4e457d4","tid":795324,"uid":119210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T03:53:34.000Z","msg":"見佢又大屋又跑車 唔知堅定流"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T03:55:34.000Z","msg":"社會上越有錢就越低調!!!!  反其道而行個D 都係吹出黎搭雞棚呃個班貪心既無知撚, 你睇之前俾人拉哂個班MK 倫敦金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T04:03:18.000Z","msg":"呢個真<br />\n唔通真係自己賺夠想俾大家賺下咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T04:09:22.000Z","msg":"貪心既人最易呃...!"},{"pid":"26a86196b05665ffe263bbbeb0013a52af701eb9","tid":795324,"uid":119210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b869707be0b56f3fd77dc2ddc52c8bccd7e65a5","tid":795324,"uid":36138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"789a8370d31b2008d1dca3eeef67ae4aa4e457d4","tid":795324,"uid":119210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d424cf748c3c70e7414f928aa4a1cf2c42bbb0b","tid":795324,"uid":165404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T03:51:49.000Z","msg":"幣少成日吹奏自己唔係呢種，唔知真定假"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T03:53:34.000Z","msg":"見佢又大屋又跑車 唔知堅定流"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T03:55:34.000Z","msg":"社會上越有錢就越低調!!!!  反其道而行個D 都係吹出黎搭雞棚呃個班貪心既無知撚, 你睇之前俾人拉哂個班MK 倫敦金<img src=\"/asset